data.title: Jennifer Goicoechea - Age, Family, Bio
data.meta_description: Jennifer Goicoechea: her birthday, what she did before fame, her family life, fun trivia facts, popularity rankings, and more.
data.text:
About

Business executive who became known for being the wife of R&B singer Usher. She is popular on social media and her Instagram account has over 130,000 followers.

Before Fame

She is the Vice President of A&R at Epic Records.

Trivia

She has driven across the country in an RV and documented the trip on her Instagram. Her management company is called Boogs'N'Effect Management.

Family Life

She was born and raised in Miami, Florida. She and Usher are the parents of two children. Their daughter is named Sovereign and was born in October 2019. Their son is named Sire Castrello Raymond and was born in September 2021. They got engaged in August 2022 and married in February 2024.
